# Tech Stack & Conventions

## 1. Core Stack
- **Framework:** React Router v7 (SSR + CSR Hybrid)
- **Language:** TypeScript
- **Runtime:** Node.js
- **Package Manager:** npm

## 2. Frontend
- **UI Library:** React 19
- **Styling:** Tailwind CSS v4
- **Components:** Radix UI (Primitives), Lucide React (Icons)
- **State Management:** React Context + Hooks (Feature-based)
- **Form Handling:** Standard React forms / Hooks.

## 3. Backend & Database
- **BaaS:** Supabase
- **Auth:** Supabase Auth
- **Database:** PostgreSQL
- **ORM:** Drizzle ORM (`drizzle-orm`, `drizzle-kit`)
- **API Communication:** Supabase Client (`@supabase/supabase-js`)

## 4. Tools & Testing
- **Bundler:** Vite
- **E2E Testing:** Playwright
- **Linting/Formatting:** Prettier

## 5. Directory Structure Convention
- `app/features/`: Domain-based feature modules (auth, phraselog, users, etc.)
- `app/core/`: Shared components and utilities.
- `app/routes/`: Route definitions (React Router v7).
